name: Gemini 2.5 Deep Think
description: First hybrid reasoning model with parallel thinking techniques. Uses extended reasoning for complex problem-solving, generating and evaluating multiple ideas simultaneously.
notes: MoE transformer architecture. Can generate up to 192K output tokens. Achieves Bronze-level on IMO 2025 benchmark. State-of-the-art on LiveCodeBench V6 and Humanity's Last Exam. Automatically uses code execution and Google Search tools.
